fields.Title: YARD / CUNO BODY
fields.Description: * Ask Cuno about the hanged man.

fields.Title: You: "(Whisper.)  "Kim, help me out here...."
fields.Dialogue Text: (Whisper.)  "Kim, help me out here. What do we want to know?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Just a lone pig trying to sugar-ta..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Just a lone pig trying to sugar-talk some kids. That seems pretty fucking suspicious to Cuno."

fields.Title: Drama: "He's trying to hide the fact that h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's trying to hide the fact that he doesn't know.

fields.Title: Drama: "The city's too large for him to hav..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The city's too large for him to have left. But he wasn't *here* either... So where was he?

fields.Title: Logic: "This is a minor discovery. Don't le..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is a minor discovery. Don't let this Night City business clog up your mind. Proceed with your investigation. If it's really important, it will come up later.

fields.Title: Logic: "It's impossible to deduce what it *..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's impossible to deduce what it *is* about, at least for the moment. If it's important, it'll come up later. Focus on the case.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno's fuck-gimp's got one big thi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno's fuck-gimp's got one big thing wrong with him. He's a fucking mutant."
fields.Alternate1: "That fuck-gimp had one thing majorly wrong with him -- he's a fucking mutant."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""So yeah, he's the one you wanna ta..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So yeah, he's the one you wanna talk to. He's fucking crazy about that armour shit. Coming here, pretending like he likes cows, tryin'a catch a peep at Cuno's armour... Go to the gates -- ask him yourself."

fields.Title: Suggestion: "You have no idea what the *usual* i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You have no idea what the *usual* is. Just ask whatever comes to mind.

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Pig's choking, he's totally chokin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Pig's choking, he's totally choking!"

fields.Title: You: ""Do you know how it got up there?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you know how it got up there?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""That's the name of Cuno's city, bi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That's the name of Cuno's city, bitch! Get the fuck off Cuno's back. This shit ain't about that."

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Watch out, Cuno, he's trying to re..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Watch out, Cuno, he's trying to relate to you!"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Get the fuck out of here, tryin'a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Get the fuck out of here, tryin'a fuck on me with that midget shit? Cuno's twelve! He's huge!" He squints at you.

fields.Title: Visual Calculus: "Yes, you met him at the gates. The..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yes, you met him at the gates. The one with the boots and the jolly smile.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You wanna know where Cuno was? You..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You wanna know where Cuno was? You wanna know what Cuno's been fucking *up* to?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Why don't you figure your shit out..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why don't you figure your shit out yourself -- before you come to *Detective Cuno* for help?"

fields.Title: You: ""And you're just telling me this ou..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "And you're just telling me this out of the kindness of your heart, Cuno?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, Cuno's doing charity today...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, Cuno's doing charity today. Cuno Day. Cuno feels *sorry* for you, loser-pig. Cuno's doing pity now."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""The fuck about it?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "The fuck about it?"

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Fucking idiot *mulkkupää* doesn't..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fucking idiot *mulkkupää* doesn't know any questions."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Just a couple of pigs sniffing aro..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Just a couple of pigs sniffing around in the dirt. That seems pretty fucking suspicious to Cuno."

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "He could've just said he doesn't kn..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He could've just said he doesn't know.

fields.Title: You: ""Okay.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay."

fields.Title: Logic: "Thanks, Cuno. That's one name you c..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Thanks, Cuno. That's one name you can now cross off the list.

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Don't tell him that Cuno, it's lam..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't tell him that Cuno, it's lame!"

fields.Title: You: ""A contusion is a bruise. I'm talki..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "A contusion is a bruise. I'm talking about the marks your stones left on the corpse."

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "Got told by a twelve-year old. Here..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Got told by a twelve-year old. Here's a tip for the future: If you wanna win an argument, wait for my sign. Don't just go barging in.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Shoot that shit at Cuno.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Shoot that shit at Cuno."

fields.Title: You: ""You threw it in the sea?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You threw it in the sea?"

fields.Title: You: ""I meant who he *was*. Before he di..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I meant who he *was*. Before he died?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Mesque, or... or I don't know. Som..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Mesque, or... or I don't know. Some other place... Night City! Cuno was in fucking Night City."

fields.Title: Cuno: "He drills his temples with his fing..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He drills his temples with his fingers in some strange, aggressive gesture. "Cuno doesn't give a shit about that freak armour. Cuno threw that shit away."

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Yeah, you tell the *fägäri*, Cuno!""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, you tell the *fägäri*, Cuno!"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno's fuck-gimp." He picks up a r..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno's fuck-gimp." He picks up a rock. "Cuno uses the fuck-gimp for target practice."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno knows all kinds of shit. Cuno..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno knows all kinds of shit. Cuno's not a snitch, that's all." He shakes his head, clearly offended. "Tryin'a make the Cuno sing into the popophone..."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno *knows* shit. Cuno's not a sn..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno *knows* shit. Cuno's not a snitch, that's all." He shakes his head, clearly offended. "Tryin'a make Cuno sing into the popophone..."

fields.Title: Drama: "Stop choking or everyone will see y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Stop choking or everyone will see you're a fake! All this *thespianism* isn't doing you any good!

fields.Title: You: ""Where is Night City?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Where is Night City?"

fields.Title: Cuno: "Cuno erupts into laughter, pointing..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Cuno erupts into laughter, pointing his finger at you, then Kim, then back at you...

fields.Title: You: ""You mean Mañana?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "You mean Mañana?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Remember Night City, pig fuck? Cun..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Remember Night City, pig fuck? Cuno was in fucking Night City getting shit *done*."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You heard Cuno -- Cuno wasn't even..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You heard Cuno -- Cuno wasn't even in Martinaise. Cuno wasn't in Revachol." He puffs himself up. "Cuno wasn't *regional*."

fields.Title: You: ""Where's the rest of his armour?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Where's the rest of his armour?"
fields.Alternate1: "Where's the rest of his armour? Besides his cuirass. I got that."

fields.Title: Interfacing: "What the hell *is* it about then? A..."
fields.Dialogue Text: What the hell *is* it about then? A city of toys? No, with this kid, it's probably made of cigarette butts. Or maybe sand and melting snow?

fields.Title: Logic: "Has Cuno been to some kind of schoo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Has Cuno been to some kind of school? Probably a school for children with behavioural difficulties.

fields.Title: You: ""How come?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "How come?"

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Trying to fuck on Cuno? Fuck outta..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Trying to fuck on Cuno? Fuck outta here!"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, he's the one you wanna talk..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, he's the one you wanna talk to. He's fucking crazy about that armour shit. Coming here, pretending like he likes cows, tryin'a catch a peep at Cuno's armour."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""If I were to want to waste my time..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "If I were to want to waste my time -- which I do not -- I would ask them who he is, how he got there, and the *usual*."

fields.Title: You: ""Have you seen anyone suspicious ar..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Have you seen anyone suspicious around?"

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "An unfortunate choice of words, the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: An unfortunate choice of words, the lieutenant from Precinct 57 thinks. He looks downwind at the rotting corpse. He could use a cigarette right about now.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Hmmm... maybe we should." The lieu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hmmm... maybe we should." The lieutenant raises an eyebrow.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno kicked that shit in the sea...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno kicked that shit in the sea. Rugby style. That shit means *nothing* to Cuno."

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "End of conversation. Very strong. Y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: End of conversation. Very strong. You should be this stoic.

fields.Title: You: ""So you didn't see it happening?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "So you didn't see it happening?"

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "The usual being "have you seen anyt..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The usual being "have you seen anything out of the ordinary" or "have you seen anything suspicious"?

fields.Title: Cuno: ""It's not fucking lame! Cuno's buil..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's not fucking lame! Cuno's building Cuno's city -- Night City, Rage City, the City of Rage. That's it. And it's not lame!"

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Lame!""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Lame!"

fields.Title: You: ""Yes, that's what I'm saying. You'r..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes, that's what I'm saying. You're stupid."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Look at him!" He points to the bod..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Look at him!" He points to the body. "Fucking growth hormone shit. He's a giant. The armour's too big for *any man*."

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Don't tell the pig shit, Cuno!""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't tell the pig shit, Cuno!"

fields.Title: You: ""Do you know who he was?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you know who he was?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Fucking Mesque, or I don't know. S..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fucking Mesque, or I don't know. Some other place... Night City! Cuno was in fucking Night City."

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): ""Hmmm..." you hear the lieutenant h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hmmm..." you hear the lieutenant hum.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, that shit means *nothing* to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, that shit means *nothing* to Cuno," he repeats. "Cuno doesn't give a shit about material shit. Cuno's a fucking monk!"

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Yes. This troubadour has it. You ca..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yes. This troubadour has it. You can *feel* it.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah? Cuno didn't smoke him, if th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah? Cuno didn't smoke him, if that's what you mean." He draws snot up his nose.

fields.Title: You: "Better not to mention it."
fields.Dialogue Text: Better not to mention it.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno doesn't give a shit about the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno doesn't give a shit about the armour."

fields.Title: You: ""A mutant?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "A mutant?"

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "Oh, come on. He's just pretending t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Oh, come on. He's just pretending that he doesn't care because he's too small for the armour.

fields.Title: You: ""What do you mean you *threw it awa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you mean you *threw it away*?"

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "He means Mañana, the laid-back stri..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He means Mañana, the laid-back striker at the gates.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Shitload, pig, what's your questio..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Shitload, pig, what's your question?"

fields.Title: Reaction Speed: "This is where you *quickly* ask him..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is where you *quickly* ask him questions. Real cop-questions. Like a cop.

fields.Title: You: ""You could've just said you don't k..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You could've just said you don't know."

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Pigs come to take you back, Cuno!"..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Pigs come to take you back, Cuno!" the hat-wearing fiend shrieks. "Tryin'a dig up dirt on you!"

fields.Title: You: ""You're just too small for the armo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're just too small for the armour."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You're testing Cuno's patience her..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're testing Cuno's patience here."

fields.Title: You: ""Oh, okay. Where did you go then?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, okay. Where did you go then?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Probably climbed? Cuno was busy *d..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Probably climbed? Cuno was busy *down the road* when that shit went down."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Told you, pig bacon. Cuno doesn't..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Told you, pig bacon. Cuno doesn't do regional. Cuno's been to places you wouldn't dream of."

fields.Title: Authority: "The kids are overwhelming you. Rega..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The kids are overwhelming you. Regain control of yourself and the situation.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno doesn't give a shit about you..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno doesn't give a shit about your handicap. Get a wheelchair or something. Cuno doesn't care."

fields.Title: Logic: "How is that better? At least get ba..."
fields.Dialogue Text: How is that better? At least get back to the corpse then.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno gives this info out on a need..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno gives this info out on a need-to-know basis. And *you* don't need to know." He draws snot up his nose. "Cuno didn't smoke the gimp, if that's what you meant."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Do you remember how he looked?! Fu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you remember how he looked?! Fucking growth hormone shit. He's a giant. The armour's too big for *any man*."

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "The lieutenant is sitting on the ed..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant is sitting on the edge of his bed, twenty kilometres from here, and cleaning his boots. An archetypal policeman like him would *definitely* come up with some questions to ask right now. Unlike you, standing here alone, unable to gather your thoughts.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah it's fucking okay!" He throws..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah it's fucking okay!" He throws the rock. It misses. "Gotta have a gimp for rock practice..."

fields.Title: Cuno: "The buck-toothed gremlin lets go of..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The buck-toothed gremlin lets go of his head. Looks like the attack has passed.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""I don't know, some fucking..." He..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know, some fucking..." He looks around, trying to come up with something.

fields.Title: You: ""That's a fictional city name. Nigh..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That's a fictional city name. Night City doesn't exist."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Why you gotta be riding Cuno's ass..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why you gotta be riding Cuno's ass? You haven't been where Cuno's been. You haven't been in Cuno's head."

fields.Title: You: ""I hate words too.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I hate words too."

fields.Title: You: "Proceed with the questioning."
fields.Dialogue Text: Proceed with the questioning.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Words are fucking shit, make you s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Words are fucking shit, make you stupid!" He spits on the ground. "Cuno's got his own words now -- Cuno-words."

fields.Title: You: ""Cuno, shouldn't you be at school o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno, shouldn't you be at school or something?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno tried to get the helmet on. I..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno tried to get the helmet on. It was too big." He performs a kick-off on the imaginary helmet.

fields.Title: You: ""You didn't really leave the city...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You didn't really leave the city. Where were you?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Oh, did Cuno make your shit-sniffi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, did Cuno make your shit-sniffing harder? Obstruction of shit-sniffing?" He lets go of his head, suddenly feeling better. "This is Cuno's Kingdom. Cuno fucking rules here."

fields.Title: You: ""So you don't know anything.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "So you don't know anything."

fields.Title: You: ""Okay. About the dead body...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay. About the dead body..."

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "There is no Night City anywhere. Th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There is no Night City anywhere. That sounds like the name of a city in some pulp science fiction novel.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Fuck are you talking about? What i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fuck are you talking about? What is this *con-tush-on* shit?" He grabs his head like it's suddenly hurting.

fields.Title: Drama: "Yes, pray pardon, sire! Better to l..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yes, pray pardon, sire! Better to let it be. I did not mean to make you paranoid.

fields.Title: Cuno: "He drills his temples with his fing..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He drills his temples with his fingers in some strange, aggressive gesture. "Cuno doesn't give a shit about that freak armour. Cuno threw that shit away."

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""What the fuck, Cuno! Stop being so..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What the fuck, Cuno! Stop being so fucking lame!"

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Get lost, f****t!""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Get lost, f****t!"

fields.Title: You: ""More on this later. Right now let'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "More on this later. Right now let's talk about something else."

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "The pain of the word recedes, he's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The pain of the word recedes, he's feeling better now. Further away from *education*.

fields.Title: You: ""Okay, another question then.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay, another question then."

fields.Title: You: ""Who do you mean, troubadour?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Who do you mean, troubadour?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, Cock-in-Boots. You know that..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, Cock-in-Boots. You know that jolly Union cow fucker? Came around talking about cows or some shit. Came around pretendin' like he cares about cows."

fields.Title: You: ""I don't have questions.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't have questions."

fields.Title: You: ""There are contusions all over his..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There are contusions all over his body. Did you do that?"

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "He's thinking the kid has amassed q..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's thinking the kid has amassed quite the vocabulary of law-enforcement terms. But he's not going to stick his nose into this.

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Me and *my* partner are wondering...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Me and *my* partner are wondering..." The demonic hiss behind the fence gets louder. "Do you guys puff Peter?"

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "Good. That's what the lieutenant fr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Good. That's what the lieutenant from Precinct 57 would have done as well.

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""They're lost without you, Cuno! Th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "They're lost without you, Cuno! They need you. You're in control of this!"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""You wanna fuck on someone 'bout th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You wanna fuck on someone 'bout that armour? Go fuck the moustached Union fuck -- the jolly troubadour shit at the gates."

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""He says you're *stupid*, Cuno! The..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He says you're *stupid*, Cuno! They want to make you stupid again!"

fields.Title: You: ""Me and my partner are wondering, w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Me and my partner are wondering, where did you pick up so many police terms?"

fields.Title: Suggestion: "It's tough to tell, but he actually..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's tough to tell, but he actually does... a little. He tilts his head to the right, reassessing you in the light of your bad ass learning disability.

fields.Title: Cuno: "Cuno lets go of his head. "Get the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Cuno lets go of his head. "Get the fuck out of here, calling Cuno stupid? Pigs come to Cuno for guidance, then say he's stupid? The fuck is up with that?"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""What are you... fucking eighty? Wh..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What are you... fucking eighty? When Cuno's eighty, Cuno can fit four of you in Cuno! Fuck outta here!"

fields.Title: Drama: "Curious, my liege. Why did Cuno fee..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Curious, my liege. Why did Cuno feed you this information?

fields.Title: You: "Let it be."
fields.Dialogue Text: Let it be.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno knows what you meant. Cuno's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno knows what you meant. Cuno's not a snitch, that's all." He shakes his head, clearly offended. "Tryin'a make Cuno sing into the popophone..."

fields.Title: Cunoesse: ""Don't ask the pigs for permission,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Don't ask the pigs for permission, Cuno. Don't ask the pigs for shit!"

fields.Title: You: ""Let's back up. This isn't going an..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Let's back up. This isn't going anywhere."

fields.Title: Rhetoric: "Looks like you're a *fägäri* now, w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Looks like you're a *fägäri* now, whatever that means. The *suspicious* question doesn't really work in antagonistic situations.

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "An unfortunate choice of words, the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: An unfortunate choice of words, the lieutenant from Precinct 57 thinks. He looks at the harbour walls looming overhead. He could use a cigarette right about now.

fields.Title: You: ""I have behavioural difficulties to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I have behavioural difficulties too."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""That's the past, pig. Cuno's not *..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That's the past, pig. Cuno's not *there* anymore. Cuno did his time." He nods solemnly. "Now ask about that pig corpse shit and don't go sniffing into Cuno's past!"

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, Cuno's doing charity today...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, Cuno's doing charity today. Cuno Day. Cuno feels *sorry* for you two loser-pigs. Cuno's doing pity now."

fields.Title: Drama: "Still, seems suspicious... He may h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Still, seems suspicious... He may have it in for that guy. Or you may be paranoid. That is also a possibility, sire.
